| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3855 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6e4ef500-e248-5869-9dc5-ec559be904a6"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
